title: Announcement
message: Hey, it’s me the Coach! I’m Back and I opened a new gym but this time kid no more slacking around. I need you in top shape so we can win the Gold Medal! I know you’ve enjoyed The Thrill Of The Fight 1 but it’s time we take it to the next level get The Thrill Of The Fight 2 and start your new amateur career kid! See you on the other side!
